      <title>阿迪達斯股價飆升，強勁勢頭助力第一季業績好轉，引發展望上調</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-surges-strong-momentum-helps-q1-beat-triggers-outlook-hike-2024-04-17/</link>
